# DEMON - unix daemon network                  

# LIFECYCLES #######################################
# awareness of self_state, host_state & network_state
Work que
Get FACE by dtrace-probes analysis of self_state
Get FACE by top anaylysis in host_enviornment
scp FACE and get input on net_clan
Work que

# FACE #############################################
AGE_IN_HOURS
SUCCESS_ITERATIONS
NAME
GEAR (mem, nice, threads)
STATE (dtrace)

# API ##############################################
sha - sha256 file
blkr - chop file to even parts
slicr - chop file to odd parts
get - http data extraction
xtrac - archive extraction
vkey - verify key files created by blkr/slicr
regx - test contents
krip - encrypt file

